## AI-Facing Endpoints

{{- if .WithInteraction }}
- `POST /mcp` ‚Äî MCP JSON-RPC endpoint (protocol version 2025-06-18)
  - `initialize` ‚Äî capability negotiation and server info
  - `ping` ‚Äî liveness check
  - `tools/list` / `tools/call` ‚Äî discover and invoke service methods
  - `resources/list` / `resources/read` ‚Äî read server-exposed data artifacts
  - `resources/templates/list` ‚Äî discover parameterised resource URI patterns
  - `prompts/list` / `prompts/get` ‚Äî list and render reusable prompt templates
  - `completion/complete` ‚Äî auto-complete prompt argument values
  - `logging/setLevel` ‚Äî adjust server log verbosity
  - `notifications/initialized` ‚Äî complete the MCP handshake (notification, no response)
  - Supports Streamable HTTP transport: GET for SSE streams, DELETE for session termination
  - Supports MCP Sampling: server can request LLM completions from connected clients
  - Server-initiated notifications: tools/list_changed, prompts/list_changed, resources/list_changed, resources/updated, message, progress
{{- end }}
{{- if .WithSkill }}
- `GET /skill` ‚Äî OpenAI-style tool discovery
- `GET /skill?format=mcp` ‚Äî MCP-style tool discovery (schema only)
{{- end }}
{{- if .WithOpenAPI }}
- `GET /openapi.json` ‚Äî generated OpenAPI 3.1 contract
- `GET /swagger/` ‚Äî Swagger UI backed by the generated contract
{{- end }}
- `GET /debug/routes` ‚Äî runtime route inspection
- `GET /health` ‚Äî health check

## Common Modifications

1. **Add business logic** ‚Üí edit `service/<name>/service.go`
2. **Add endpoint middleware** ‚Üí edit `endpoint/<name>/custom_chain.go`
3. **Add a new service or model** ‚Üí run `microgen extend -check -out .` first, then use `-append-service` or `-append-model`
4. **Change AI tool behavior** ‚Üí the tools are auto-registered from endpoints; change the underlying service logic instead

